        "ggOKNXI3QFQ_text": "Your Glow-Up Starts Here — Just Like Theirs",
        "gg2fiKAtE2B_text": "<p>Here’s what real women have to say about the mask that fits their lifestyle:</p>",
        "ggjsA0lRbX__text": "<p>“I was hesitant to try anything new at 53, but this mask didn’t irritate my sensitive skin at all. It softened my laugh lines and gave me a healthy glow the next morning.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>—&nbsp;MARIA T., 53</strong></p>",
        "ggS2MK_shOw_text": "<p>“After juggling work and family, I barely had time for self-care. This mask made it easy. Just once a week and my skin feels hydrated and alive again.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>—&nbsp;JANELLE R., 41</strong></p>",
        "ggE7iiaEa0-_text": "<p>“I’m post-menopause, and my skin became dry and dull. This mask brought back a glow I hadn’t seen in years. Even my daughter noticed!”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>—&nbsp;DIANE L., 59</strong></p>",
        "ggBUjnIoryo_text": "<p>“The mask helps me feel put together, even when I don’t wear makeup. It’s my go-to before events or long work days. I wish I found it sooner.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>—&nbsp;RACHEL M., 47</strong></p>",
